OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,FYoung people in Wales will be offered
OL,7,Fthe Meningococcal B (MenB) vaccine for
OL,8,Fthe first time as part of a temporary
OL,9,Fvaccination programme beginning later
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,FThe initiative follows a series of
OL,13,Foutbreaks across the UK, including an
OL,14,Foutbreak among students at the
OL,15,FUniversity of Kent in March 2026 and
OL,16,Fseveral other clusters reported
OL,17,Foutside the usual seasonal pattern.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
