OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,FMeningococcal B is the leading cause
OL,7,Fof invasive meningococcal disease, an
OL,8,Finfection which can lead to meningitis
OL,9,Fand sepsis, both of which can develop
OL,10,Frapidly and may be life-threatening.
OL,12,FHealth officials say young people are
OL,13,Fat a higher risk of contracting the
OL,14,Fdisease, particularly those entering
OL,15,Fhigher education environments where
OL,16,Fclose social contact and communal
OL,17,Fliving can increase transmission.
OL,19,FThe vaccination programme will run
OL,20,Ffrom July to December 2026.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
