CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,FIt will be available to all young
OL,7,Fpeople aged 17 and 18 who were born
OL,8,Fbetween 1 September 2007 and 31 August
OL,9,F2008.
OL,11,FThe offer will also extend to
OL,12,Findividuals aged 18 to 25 who are
OL,13,Fentering higher education or
OL,14,Fresidential further education for the
OL,15,Ffirst time in autumn 2026, including
OL,16,Finternational students.
OL,18,FThe vaccine will be administered in
OL,19,Ftwo doses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
