CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,FThose aged 17 and 18 will receive
OL,7,Finvitation letters from their local
OL,8,Fhealth boards from 6 July, outlining
OL,9,Fhow to book an appointment. Eligible
OL,10,Fstudents aged 18 to 25 will be
OL,11,Frequired to contact their health board
OL,12,Ffrom 20 July for further information
OL,13,Fabout accessing the vaccine.
OL,15,FLana Quinlan, 22, contracted
OL,16,FMeningitis B in 2022. Lana was due to
OL,17,Fmove to Cardiff University the same
OL,18,Fweek, but spent the first month of her
OL,19,Fhigher education journey in hospital.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
