OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,FShe has since campaigned for the
OL,7,Fvaccine roll out.
OL,9,FResponding to the announcement, Lana
OL,10,Fsaid: "It's really upsetting that it
OL,11,Ftook such a huge event for the change
OL,12,Fto happen."
OL,14,FHowever, she said the vaccination
OL,15,Fbeing part of a 'one-off' scheme
OL,16,F'doesn't make sense'.
OL,26,@rD@GOUtD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
