OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,F"When you talk about vaccinating one
OL,7,Fgeneration, you need everyone in the
OL,8,Funiversities and for it to happen
OL,9,Fevery year... so it prevents anything
OL,10,Flike this happening in the future."
OL,12,FDeputy Minister for Public and
OL,13,FPreventative Health Nerys Evans
OL,14,Fdescribed meningococcal B as a 'rare'
OL,15,Fbut 'serious disease'.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
