PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,FShe said: "Following recent outbreaks
OL,7,Facross the UK, the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fhas acted decisively to ensure that
OL,9,Fyoung people in Wales will be offered
OL,10,Fthis additional protection and I urge
OL,11,Feveryone who is eligible to take up
OL,12,Ftheir vaccination offer."
OL,14,FWales' Chief Medical Officer,
OL,15,FProfessor Isabel Oliver, said: "This
OL,16,Fis a safe and effective vaccine that
OL,17,Fwill offer important protection to
OL,18,Fthose who receive it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1781513302
OL,3,CMeningitis B vaccine to be rolled out
OL,4,Cto young people
OL,6,F"With the new academic year
OL,7,Fapproaching, it is vital that eligible
OL,8,Fyoung people come forward for both
OL,9,Fdoses as soon as the programme opens.
OL,10,FI encourage all those who qualify to
OL,11,Fact promptly."
OL,13,FDr Christopher Johnson, Head of
OL,14,FVaccine Preventable Disease Programme
OL,15,Fat Public Health Wales said: "Young
OL,16,Fpeople heading to university for the
OL,17,Ffirst time are at an elevated risk of
OL,18,FMeningitis B, as they mix with new
OL,19,Fgroups of people while enjoying their
OL,20,Fnew environment.
OL,26,@wD@^OU
